item.title: Malford Milligan-On the Way to Calvary
item.description:
Malford Milligan-On the Way to Calvary

I recently had the pleasure of sitting in with soul, blues and rock singer Malford Milligan, who has been compared to Otis Redding and Al Green. We played a couple of classic blues tunes, a real blast. I hope you enjoy the two tunes I've uploaded.

item.title: Riding the Light
item.description:
Riding the Light

Take a soaring journey across Austin, the Live Music Capital of the World. Shot in the winter of 2014-2013, "Riding the Light" presents the Austin skyline as you've never seen it before. I'm excited and proud to share this short film, my third solo hyperlapse cityscape project.

item.title: Austin City Limits Celebrates 40 Years "Not Fade Away"
item.description:
Austin City Limits Celebrates 40 Years "Not Fade Away"

An all-star lineup celebrating four decades of Austin City Limits culminates in Buddy Holly's classic "Not Fade Away." Watch the special on Friday, October 3rd on PBS at 9E/8C.
